{"000-section": {"000-title": "Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana Gramin 2017-18 \u2013 51 Lakh Homes to be Constructed", "001-normal": "As per the SECC-2011 data, the government has surveyed about 3.92 Crore homeless families out of which 2.26 Crore have been found eligible for the scheme. [PMAY-G](https://sarkariyojana.com/pradhan-mantri-awas-yojana-gramin/) scheme is aimed at constructing 3 Crore homes in next 7 years.", "002-normal": "Central government has earmarked Rs. 15000 Crore for the implementation of PMAY-G in 2017-18. The financial benefit under the scheme has also been increased from Rs. 75000 to 1.20 Lakh along with increase in overall area from 22 Square meter to 25 square meter. The scheme would be linked with Swachch Bharat Abhiyan under which an additional amount of Rs. 12000 would be provided to construct toilet would also be provided.", "003-normal": "Apart from all this, a provision of 90/95 days of unskilled wage labour under MGNREGA over and above the unit cost is also there under the scheme which will provide benefits of about Rs. 18000 per family."}}